    <title>Water contributor: Laura Paskus</title>
    <description>Laura Paskus is an environment reporter for New Mexico Political Report. She has been writing about New Mexico’s natural resources and communities since 2002, as an assistant editor of High Country News, a radio producer at KUNM-FM, managing editor of Tribal College Journal and a freelancer for a variety of publications including the Santa Fe Reporter, New Mexico In Depth and Indian Country Today.
</description>
